{"tid":2044491,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"招有興趣參與電影製作者入Group","createTime":"2020-05-31T06:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T16:01:14.000Z","uid":343680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89c4d9c4a7e8cec3ef4b240d88abbb3c9f0d5289","tid":2044491,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"Hi ，我係一個有志於加入電影製作者（雖然我不是圈內人）<br />\n雖然好多人好多Post都話，香港電影無得攪/困局一個<br />\n但係我相信，有危先有機，呢個世界係唔會有真正絕路，只要你相信，一起走，總會走到一條出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳，我想開一個group，讓有志參與電之士/ 電影工作者 <br />\n一齊交流，一齊Brain Storming，大家傾下未來想行既路，實現一D project出來咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單打獨鬥從來都係好困難，特別係攪電影呢D群體性工作<br />\n所以我希望組織一班人/一個團隊出來，共同做一D野，希望對呢個電影圈/觀眾/世界係有價值！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣一起交流，請入呢個tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OLDPMxmW97HJhNKwDcr7IQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOLDPMxmW97HJhNKwDcr7IQ&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=e5a7e0fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OLDPMxmW97HJhNKwDcr7IQ</a>"},{"pid":"f6e72e1c79dbbc23f4116df1a0c5dee3b2c07701","tid":2044491,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b8e29dfb414d33af05ff9064638c88a5effb2a","tid":2044491,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a5f5487be751b50dd1f5e748af41ad0d8d99ce","tid":2044491,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":